@startuml agent-lifecycle
' Agent (persistent mode) state machine.
' Source of truth: docs/src/controller/agent-lifecycle.md
!include _style.puml

' ---- Happy path + idle/hibernate cycle ----
state "Pending" as Pending
state "Provisioning" as Provisioning
state "Running" as Running
state "Idle" as Idle
state "Hibernating" as Hibernating
state "Hibernated" as Hibernated
state "Resuming" as Resuming

[*] --> Pending
Pending --> Provisioning : references validated,\nclass resolved
Provisioning --> Running : Pod becomes Ready
Running --> Idle : idleTimeout elapsed
Idle --> Running : activity observed
Idle --> Hibernating : hibernationEnabled=true\nAND idle for hibernationDelay
Hibernating --> Hibernated : pod scaled to 0,\nPVC retained
Hibernated --> Resuming : channel message via User Gateway\nOR manual wake annotation
Resuming --> Running : pod Ready

' ---- Re-provisioning (spec drift / disruption) ----
Running -[#0D47A1]-> Provisioning : spec drift (Agent or AgentClass)\nOR involuntary Pod disruption
Idle -[#0D47A1]-> Provisioning : spec drift (Agent or AgentClass)\nOR involuntary Pod disruption

note left of Provisioning
  creating Pod/PVC/Service
  ....
  re-provisioning is recreate-and-clamp:
  Pod replaced, PVC/Service/Certificate
  preserved
end note
note right of Hibernating : scaling pod to zero
note right of Resuming : scaling pod back up

' ---- Branches available from any phase ----
state "any phase" as AnyPhase #F5F5F5
state "Degraded" as Degraded
state "Failed" as Failed
state "Terminating" as Terminating

AnyPhase --> Degraded : AgentClass-vs-Agent-spec mismatch\n(at Pending on initial provisioning, OR introduced\nby class or ModelProvider drift while in\nRunning/Idle/Resuming; Hibernated agents defer\nthe check to next wake) at any point
AnyPhase --> Failed : irrecoverable error\nat any point
AnyPhase --> Terminating : deletion requested\nat any point

note right of Degraded : re-enters status.preDegradedPhase\nwhen resolved
note right of Terminating : resource removed\nafter finalizers run
note bottom of AnyPhase
  Not a phase change: transient provider unhealthy
  and budget exhaustion set a Degraded CONDITION
  on the Agent with status.phase preserved.
  See Errors, Events, and Testing.
end note

' ---- Layout hints ----
Resuming -[hidden]-> AnyPhase
@enduml
